summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electric underground distribution easements over portions of Bryn Mawr; Crowell's Addition to the City of Seattle; Gunther's Lake Burien Homesites; Burke's Second Addition to the City of Seattle; Olympic Manor, Division \#2; all around view addition to the City of Seattle; Richmond Highland Addition; and northwest quarter of Section 8, Township 26 North, Range 4 East.
